Class QueryPlaylistsWindow

  • Object
    • QueryPlaylistsWindow

  • public class QueryPlaylistsWindow
extends Object
    Class that handles the query playlists window. This window allows the user to compare a set of playlists. For example, this can be used to find intersecting tracks on multiple playlists.
    Author:
    Jon
